title: I DO NOT believe Durianrider is "A Narcissist" (N.P.D.)
description: People with N.P.D. are not comic-book villains (like "The Joker" dueling with Batman), they're real human beings, struggling with a mental disorder: a "diagnosis" of this kind should not be used as a weapon to slander and humiliate someone —not even when it is a REAL diagnosis (let alone an "internet diagnosis" made up on the basis of youtube clips selected by a biased party who is (intentionally?) ignoring evidence to the contrary).
